title: pyuic dll failed to load with Python 3.6.1
body:
I've installed the latest python version. I wanted to create a project in python with PyQt4, but I am not able to convert the *.ui file into a *.py file. It always says "ImportError(from PyQt4 import QtCore): DLL load failed: %1 is not a valid Win32-Application." And I also checked my environment variables. All seems fine to work, but I don't know why this error occurs.

Maybe the wrong Python version for this PyQt version ? Thanks for your answers, I appreciate that!
